Wala silang dahilan.

252
00:16:46,131 --> 00:16:47,298
Gano'n ba talaga sa tingin mo?

253
00:16:48,216 --> 00:16:51,261
Totoong may mga taong pinapatay.

254
00:16:51,511 --> 00:16:53,221
Pero sa palagay ko

255
00:16:53,805 --> 00:16:58,268
kailangan natin sabihin sa pulis
ang lahat ng alam natin.

256
00:16:58,351 --> 00:17:00,854
Nakakatakot na kasi talaga.

257
00:17:01,980 --> 00:17:03,189
Hindi ito ang tamang panahon.

258
00:17:03,565 --> 00:17:06,401
Kailangan nating magpakatatag.

259
00:17:06,693 --> 00:17:07,986
Paano si Byeong-jun?

260
00:17:08,361 --> 00:17:10,071
Ano'ng mangyayari sa kaniya?

261
00:17:10,155 --> 00:17:11,781
Narinig kong nilipat siya sa detention.

262
00:17:11,865 --> 00:17:14,242
Talaga bang kinuha na ng piskal ang kaso?

263
00:17:14,325 --> 00:17:16,161
Oo, tama 'yon.

264
00:17:16,244 --> 00:17:17,829
Ano'ng gagawin natin?

265
00:17:17,912 --> 00:17:18,997
Umamin siya sa krimen.

266
00:17:19,080 --> 00:17:21,791
Kawawa naman, masyado siyang mahina
