Na-yeon, sigurado ka ba
na tama ang ginagawa natin?

269
00:17:28,298 --> 00:17:33,052
Wala pang ibinabalita ang press
tungkol kay No Sang-cheon.

270
00:17:33,136 --> 00:17:34,888
Tama na 'yan.

271
00:17:34,971 --> 00:17:37,515
Dapat may balita kahit papaano

272
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:40,935
