00:17:46,566 --> 00:17:48,151
Wala naman tayong plano.

276
00:17:48,485 --> 00:17:50,153
Ano'ng sinasabi mo?

277
00:17:51,446 --> 00:17:52,530
Eh, ikaw?

278
00:17:53,156 --> 00:17:55,700
Wala kang ginawa kundi maupo rito!

279
00:17:55,784 --> 00:17:57,660
Bakit tanging si Byeong-jun lang

280
