ang tinitingnang suspek?

281
00:18:00,830 --> 00:18:02,791
Tama na 'yan.

282
00:18:03,124 --> 00:18:05,752
May lalabas na article.

283
00:18:07,629 --> 00:18:10,715
May isinulat ako sa trabaho
bago pumunta rito.

284
00:18:17,430 --> 00:18:18,932
Kailangan ko ng pumunta sa ospital.

285
00:18:27,315 --> 00:18:29,442
"BUHAY BA TALAGA SI NO SANG-CHEON?"

286
00:18:29,734 --> 00:18:32,195
Siguradong pag-uusapan
ng mga tao ang article.

287
00:18:32,737 --> 00:18:35,907
Baka kayo po ang managot, ma'am.

288
00:18:43,248 --> 00:18:44,874
Sige, bahala na.

289
00:18:48,586 --> 00:18:49,796
I-UPLOAD ANG ARTICLE?
OO

290
00:18:59,556 --> 00:19:00,557
Tapos na.

291
00:19:03,226 --> 00:19:04,352
Lumabas na ang article ko.

292
00:19:06,855 --> 00:19:10,149
Malalaman na ngayon ng mga tao
at magbabago na ang mga bagay.

293
00:19:11,317 --> 00:19:12,318
Kahit papaano...

294
00:19:13,194 --> 00:19:16,030
magbabago na ang mundo natin.

295
00:19:18,449 --> 00:19:20,577
- Ms. Cheon Na-yeon.
- Ano po 'yon?

296
00:19:20,785 --> 00:19:21,870
Titingnan na kayo ng doktor.

