445
00:28:33,087 --> 00:28:34,922
- Sige, pumasok kayo!
- Hello?

446
00:28:35,339 --> 00:28:37,091
Sabay-sabay tayo mamatay!

447
00:28:37,174 --> 00:28:39,009
Palit tayo! Hello?

